title: Every Avenue Discography
description:
[From Wikipedia page http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Every_avenue]

Every Avenue is an American pop punk band from Marysville, Michigan.

Every Avenue formed in Marysville, Michigan in 2003. They self-released two eps in 2004 and 2006 before signing to Fearless Records in 2007 and releasing an EP in the summer of that year. In February 2008, their first full-length Shh. Just Go With It was released and hit #27 on the U.S. Billboard Heatseekers chart.
